FusionInventory::Agent::Task::Deploy - Software deployment support
for FusionInvnetory Agent

DESCRIPTION
With this module, FusionInventory can accept software deployment
request from an GLPI server with the FusionInventory plugin.

This module uses SSL certificat to authentificat the server. You
may have to point --ca-cert-file or --ca-cert-dir to your public certificat.

If the P2P option is turned on, the agent will looks for peer in its
network. The network size will be limited at 255 machines.


